author: Stephanie
title: Stephanie
text: I was searching far and wide for square stickers to stick on mini champagne bottles. Officeworks, independant sticker companies etc. All were too expensive or incredibly rigid with their file types. I couldn't believe how easy and CHEAP you guys were. Will definitely use again and recommend to others.
